{"tid":2513004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何桂藍獄中書：真正當手足係condom嘅，係容忍「受難」反噬運動，成為削弱運動嘅消極言論","createTime":"2021-05-02T07:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T08:38:21.000Z","uid":74339,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b176d197e63c3c9df78a4383bba9cdd4ab82ce3b","tid":2513004,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"《容讓「受難」反噬運動 才是真正「當手足係condam」（上）》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gwynethhokl/posts/305021191131782\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgwynethhokl%2Fposts%2F305021191131782&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=ccaa66d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/gwynethhokl/posts/305021191131782</a><br />\n<br />\n（上）分咗3節，不過比較抽象，所以我嘗試理解總結一下。個人學識有限，錯係不可避免，歡迎指正。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. <br />\n「痛苦」唔一定只會連結香港人，轉化為力量，仲可能嚇窒香港人，成為阻力：<br />\n怨恨（「你哋當手足係condam」）、<br />\n迴避（「唔好用手足情緒勒索我」）、<br />\n太儒（「做咩都冇用」）、<br />\n恐懼（毋須舉例）。<br />\n<br />\n或者真正「當手足係condam」嘅，係任由呢啲消極情緒放縱，成為削弱運動嘅情感壓迫。<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n對監獄嘅恐懼限制咗人嘅想像力，以為坐監係被動結果，係不可抗衡嘅政權力量加喺無辜受難者身上。將坐監嘅手足矮化成「受難者」，坐監代表失敗或終結。<br />\n<br />\n但其實坐監可以係當事人已經了解風險，都願意企出嚟，一種主動嘅行動。<br />\n<br />\n再者，監一日未坐完，政治行動就仲未完結。<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n承接（2），將坐監嘅手足矮化為單純受難者、犧牲者，只得一片眼淚同苦難，都同樣會傷害運動。何桂藍冇闡述點傷害運動，但就舉咗啲例子，希望大家可以想像到唔同嘅「受難者」景象：<br />\n<br />\n    a)<br />\n//一個15歲的少年被判刑，法官宣判一刻，「個老母即刻喊到仆街，成個court愁雲慘霧，但我望住個𡃁仔，佢個樣係一副，我冇錯，你（指法官）先係on9嘅表情。」//<br />\n<br />\n    b)<br />\n//有一次聽審，宣判還柙完庭，犯人欄內的被告大叫「我冇做錯！」，隨即被制服押入庭內。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n《容讓「受難」反噬運動 才是真正「當手足係condam」（上）》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gwynethhokl/posts/305021191131782\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgwynethhokl%2Fposts%2F305021191131782&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=ccaa66d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/gwynethhokl/posts/305021191131782</a>"},{"pid":"cdbcea6ebd32ee6fd6e9f195d1486acc510771b0","tid":2513004,"uid":22341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:31:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd75731bb0d658fe3317d97e61b3411d7259ecb1","tid":2513004,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:32:12.000Z","msg":"時事台班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1db65ce4e1103d65857d448c722bc66656d477","tid":2513004,"uid":297848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:36:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"807a6ac0b7208c980350d78ffb86dfdc5f3b1dd8","tid":2513004,"uid":31215,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"cd75731bb0d658fe3317d97e61b3411d7259ecb1","tid":2513004,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:32:12.000Z","msg":"時事台班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:39:18.000Z","msg":"唔好胡亂標籤啦<br />\n時事台啲人好多都好反感做咩都冇用言論<br />\n<br />\n總之就係見到有呢啲特徵嘅人就要警惕<br />\n唔好理佢咩台"},{"pid":"0e5b923b26977144e789c8377eae370f445741c2","tid":2513004,"uid":10670,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd75731bb0d658fe3317d97e61b3411d7259ecb1","tid":2513004,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:32:12.000Z","msg":"時事台班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:39:22.000Z","msg":"立場姐姐係pr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac63f349d1ff49fe809f74deae5c17e23326deb","tid":2513004,"uid":74339,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cd75731bb0d658fe3317d97e61b3411d7259ecb1","tid":2513004,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime